(1558, 1, '2019-08-10 14:33:14', '2019-08-10 14:33:14', '[vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_content title=\"Commitment to Social Justice\"]The Modi Government has upheld its commitment to social justice throughout the last 48 months by empowering Divyangs and by leaving no stone unturned to ease the lives of SC and ST communities. The government has also amended legislation regarding SCs and STs to ensure swift justice in case of any violation of their rights. PM MUDRA Yojana has largely benefited SC and ST communities, with more than 50% beneficiaries belonging to the communities. Additionally, the Government has led a concerted effort in reviving the ethos of Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar by developing 5 memorials associated with his life as “Panchteerth”.[/vcode_page_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_blog title=\"Blogs\" subtitle=\"Union Ministers write about the progress in 48 months\" cat=\"35\" button=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp%2F48months%2Fblogs%2F|title:More%20Articles||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_infographics title=\"Infographics\" subtitle=\"Information and Facts You Can Share\" cat=\"20\" button=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp%2F48months%2Finfographics%2F|title:More%20Infographics||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_home_video_slider cat_voice=\"4\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Commitment to Social Justice', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'commitment-to-social-justice', '', '', '2019-08-11 05:12:59', '2019-08-11 05:12:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp/48months/?page_id=1558', 0, 'page', '', 0),
