(1567, 1, '2019-08-10 14:45:20', '2019-08-10 14:45:20', '[vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_content title=\"Harnessing Yuva Shakti\" link_video=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yaYXaQPLwXc\"]The past 48 months have witnessed many positive changes, facilitated by the Modi government for youth empowerment.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The government’s commitment to transform ten public and private educational institutions into world-renowned ones served as an impetus for the growth of the Indian youth.</li>\r\n 	<li>The priority given to higher education, particularly in the case of women, has led to socio-economic benefits.</li>\r\n 	<li>The tax relief for start-ups has also promoted employment opportunities in the country.</li>\r\n 	<li>The Modi Government has also devoted time and effort for the promotion of fitness and sports in the youth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vcode_page_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_blog title=\"Blogs\" subtitle=\"Union Ministers write about the progress in 48 months\" cat=\"38\" button=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp%2F48months%2Fblogs%2F|title:More%20Articles||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_infographics title=\"Infographics\" subtitle=\"Information and Facts You Can Share\" cat=\"23\" button=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp%2F48months%2Finfographics%2F|title:More%20Infographics||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_home_video_slider cat_voice=\"7\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Harnessing Yuva Shakti', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'harnessing-yuva-shakti', '', '', '2019-08-11 05:13:56', '2019-08-11 05:13:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp/48months/?page_id=1567', 0, 'page', '', 0),
