(1571, 1, '2019-08-10 14:48:55', '2019-08-10 14:48:55', '[vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_content title=\"Healthy India\"]Health has been one of the key issues taken up by the Modi government. In this sphere, the work done by the government in the past 48 months is commendable. The government has focused on ensuring affordable healthcare for all Indians. The National Health Protection Scheme unveiled by the Modi government which will provide up to Rs 5 lakh health coverage to families for secondary and tertiary care is a momentous step towards affordable healthcare. The establishment of wellness centres, as part of Ayushman Bharat, all over the country highlights the concern of the government regarding the vulnerable families residing in the country. Significant steps have been undertaken to ensure the elimination of tuberculosis ahead of the global target. The Modi government has left no stone unturned to provide for a healthier India by eliminating diseases, one dose at a time. The Poshan Abhiyaan implemented is the first of its kind initiative to tackle malnutrition that is prevalent in the country. The International Day of Yoga was also celebrated all over the globe which recognised the various health benefits associated with Yoga. The government, in all these months, has not once wavered in its commitment to provide quality and affordable healthcare.[/vcode_page_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_blog title=\"Blogs\" subtitle=\"Union Ministers write about the progress in 48 months\" cat=\"39\" button=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp%2F48months%2Fblogs%2F|title:More%20Articles||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_page_infographics title=\"Infographics\" subtitle=\"Information and Facts You Can Share\" cat=\"24\" button=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwp%2F48months%2Finfographics%2F|title:More%20Infographics||\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vcode_home_video_slider cat_voice=\"8\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Healthy India', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'healthy-india', '', '', '2019-08-11 05:14:00', '2019-08-11 05:14:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp/48months/?page_id=1571', 0, 'page', '', 0),
